name: CalcBeltForce
body:
### Welcome to CalcBeltForce Pages.
This program is designed for fast and accurate calculation of the traction belt operated in mine conditions for the transportation of coal and host rocks.

### Design
The interface is entirely invented by me after a long and painful interdental attempts.

### Author
